The scene is rendered in a delicate watercolor style with expressive ink outlines, combining subtle details and soft gradients for an artistic, dreamlike quality. At the top, bold yet elegant hand-drawn text reads 'Winter Wonderland,' blending seamlessly into the composition. The poster exudes a cozy, nostalgic atmosphere, perfect for a winter-themed cinematic release.
